## 🎥 Lesson 2.2.4 – DeSci vs TradSci

[![Watch the video on YouTube](https://img.youtube.com/vi/eN2TS_TytPE/0.jpg)](https://youtu.be/eN2TS_TytPE)

### 🔍 Topics covered:
- Comparison between Decentralized Science (DeSci) and Traditional Science (TradSci)
- Strengths and limitations of each system
- How DeSci addresses challenges in transparency, access, funding, and collaboration
